0.05 - Wed 07 Apr 1999 <merijn@hempseed.com>

    - Updated the README
    - Implemented ddd, dddd, mmm, mmmm (English only)
    - Enabled \n in date format. If combined with empty time
      format, formats like "dddd\nd mmm yyyy" can be used.

